<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Connexion Administrative | Forfeo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-alt">
    <div class="login-card">
        <div class="brand-logo">FORFEO</div>
        <h2>Accès Restreint</h2>
        <p>Veuillez entrer vos identifiants pour accéder à la console admin.</p>
        
        <form action="/auth" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Identifiant</label>
                <input type="text" name="username" required placeholder="Ex: admin">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Mot de passe</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" required placeholder="••••••••">
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary full-width">Se connecter au Lab</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
